00:38:56,725 --> 00:38:58,693
{\fncambria\fs22\shad2\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}The ferry just landed.

426
00:38:58,860 --> 00:39:00,851
{\fncambria\fs22\shad2\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Must be nice in Spain.
