00:40:52,442 --> 00:40:54,933
{\fncambria\fs22\shad2\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Select emergency fuel.

444
00:40:55,478 --> 00:40:57,639
{\fncambria\fs22\shad2\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Come on, you bastard!

445
00:40:58,182 --> 00:41:00,013
{\fncambria\fs22\shad2\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Come on!

446
00:41:23,340 --> 00:41:26,138
{\fncambria\fs22\shad2\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}What I'm about to say
