{\fncambria\fs22\shad2\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Just on the weekends.

467
00:42:40,518 --> 00:42:43,214
{\fncambria\fs22\shad2\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}It's my dad's place.
